<p>
		
	The "Sidebar" is a helpful tool for the work with PixPack.
	You compactly get the most important functions as well as supplementing information.
	<br/>
	It can be integrated comfortably by "bookmark" into a modern Browser, in order to access all necessary information quickly.
	<br/>
	After the integration of the sidebar it is shown when desired - similarly to a Frameset - within a separate browser left of the content frame.
	If you follow a reference from the sidebar, the reference goal is loaded in the main site.
</p>
<p>
	If you are using Netscape version 6, Mozilla 1.x, Internet Explorer version 5, Opera version 6 or Mozilla Firefox in these versions ore higher, some mouse-klicks are sufficient, in order to make the sidebar available.
</p>
<p>
	<form onsubmit="return dummy()">
		<button onclick="extra_sidebar()">Create sidebar</button>
	</form>
</p>
